# Tab Styling

- When asked to make tabs match the rest of the site, do not add spacing between sibling tabs.
- Use no inter-tab gap on standard desktop/module tab lists: prefer `gap-0`, `p-0`, or the default `TabsList` spacing unless an existing local pattern says otherwise.
- `gap-2` on `TabsTrigger` is fine for icon-to-label spacing. Avoid `gap-2` on `TabsList` unless implementing a touch/tablet wrapping layout.
- For tablet-specific wrapping tabs, only use `flex-wrap gap-2 p-1.5` when the surrounding component already branches on tablet mode.
